\u1ec1u \u0111i\u1ec1u m\u1edbi l\u1ea1 v\u00e0 b\u1ea5t ng\u1edd d\u00e0nh cho kh\u00e1n gi\u1ea3 v\u00e0 c\u00e1c nh\u00e0 s\u00e1ng t\u1ea1o n\u1ed9i dung.\n\ud83d\udd25 \u1ede m\u00f9a n\u00e0y, c\u00e1c t\u00ean tu\u1ed5i \u0111\u00ecnh \u0111\u00e1m s\u1ebd g\u00f3p m\u1eb7t trong d\u00e0n Ban gi\u00e1m kh\u1ea3o v\u00e0 C\u1ed1 v\u1ea5n chuy\u00ean m\u00f4n, bao g\u1ed3m: - Miss World Vietnam 2022 Hu\u1ef3nh Nguy\u1ec5n Mai Ph\u01b0\u01a1ng, \u0110\u1ea1o di\u1ec5n - Di\u1ec5n vi\u00ean Hu\u1ef3nh L\u1eadp, Di\u1ec5n vi\u00ean - Fashionista Qu\u1ef3nh Anh Shyn v\u00e0 Streamer - Nh\u1ea1c s\u0129 ViruSs. \n\ud83d\udd25 H\u00e3y gi\u00e0nh l\u1ea5y c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i tr\u1edf th\u00e0nh Master 2023 v\u1edbi 3 l\u0129nh v\u1ef1c thi c\u1ef1c h\u1ea5p d\u1eabn: Entertainment Master, Lifestyle Master v\u00e0 Game Master. \n\n\u27a1\ufe0f T\u00ecm hi\u1ec3u th\u00eam t\u1ea1i: https://activity.tiktok.com/magic/eco/runtime/release/64de2d98a72eb104a882e503?appType=tiktok&amp;magic_page_no=1&amp;magic_source=htcdes\n\n \nGIAI \u0110O\u1ea0N 3: CHUNG K\u1ebeT\n\n7.10.2023: K\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 th\u00ed sinh c\u00f3 l\u01b0\u1ee3t b\u00ecnh ch\u1ecdn cao nh\u1ea5t c\u1ee7a m\u1ed7i l\u0129nh v\u1ef1c v\u00e0 02 th\u00ed sinh \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c c\u1ee9u b\u1edfi nh\u00e0 t\u00e0i tr\u1ee3 cu\u1ed9c thi s\u1ebd tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng \u0111ua tranh t\u00e0i \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c c\u00f4ng b\u1ed1 t\u1ea1i trang ch\u1ee7 c\u1ee7a cu\u1ed9c thi tr\u00ean n\u1ec1n t\u1ea3ng TikTok v\u00e0 fanpage c\u1ee7a TikTok.\n\n12.10.2023: TOP 14 th\u00ed sinh xu\u1ea5t s\u1eafc nh\u1ea5t c\u1ee7a 03 l\u0129nh v\u1ef1c s\u1ebd tham gia bu\u1ed5i training c\u00f9ng H\u1ecdc vi\u1ec7n X\u00e2y d\u1ef1ng &amp; \u0110\u00e0o t\u1ea1o h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh c\u00e1 nh\u00e2n iMage Coach \u0111\u1ec3 chu\u1ea9n b\u1ecb cho ph\u1ea7n tranh t\u00e0i &amp; tr\u00ecnh di\u1ec5n t\u00e0i n\u0103ng t\u1ea1i \u0110\u00eam Chung k\u1ebft \u2013 Gala Night Master 2023 by TikTok. \n\n14.10.2023: \u0110\u00eam trao gi\u1ea3i s\u1ebd di\u1ec5n ra v\u00e0o ng\u00e0y 14/10/2023 v\u00e0 s\u1ebd \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c livestream tr\u00ean n\u1ec1n t\u1ea3ng TikTok. Ban t\u1ed5 ch\u1ee9c s\u1ebd li\u00ean h\u1ec7 v\u00e0 g\u1eedi gi\u1ea5y m\u1eddi \u0111\u1ebfn c\u00e1c th\u00ed sinh th\u1eafng gi\u1ea3i v\u1ec1 l\u1ecbch tr\u00ecnh v\u00e0 \u0111\u1ecba \u0111i\u1ec3m c\u1ee7a \u0110\u00eam trao gi\u1ea3i.\n\nD\u1ef1a v\u00e0o ph\u1ea7n thi c\u1ee7a c\u00e1c nh\u00e0 s\u00e1ng t\u1ea1o n\u1ed9i dung tr\u00ean s\u00e2n kh\u1ea5u, c\u00f9ng qu\u00e1 tr\u00ecnh th\u1ec3 hi\u1ec7n c\u1ee7a t\u1eebng th\u00ed sinh qua c\u00e1c v\u00f2ng thi c\u1ee7a Master by 2023 by TikTok, Ban gi\u00e1m kh\u1ea3o c\u00f9ng Ban t\u1ed5 ch\u1ee9c s\u1ebd ch\u1ecdn ra Qu\u00e1n qu\u00e2n c\u1ee7a m\u1ed7i l\u0129nh v\u1ef1c: Entertainment Master, Lifestyle Master &amp; Game Master. B\u00ean c\u1ea1nh \u0111\u00f3, s\u1ebd c\u00f3 m\u1ed9t gi\u1ea3i th\u01b0\u1edfng d\u00e0nh cho nh\u00e0 s\u00e1ng t\u1ea1o n\u1ed9i dung to\u00e0n n\u0103ng nh\u1ea5t \u2013 TikTok Master 2023, v\u1edbi s\u1ed1 \u0111i\u1ec3m \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c t\u00ednh t\u1eeb 50% \u0111i\u1ec3m \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 t\u1eeb BGK &amp; 50% b\u00ecnh ch\u1ecdn t\u1eeb kh\u00e1n gi\u1ea3. C\u1ed5ng b\u00ecnh ch\u1ecdn tr\u00ean trang ch\u1ee7 ch\u01b0\u01a1ng tr\u00ecnh s\u1ebd \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c m\u1edf t\u1eeb 20h00 \u2013 22h00 ngay trong Gala Night Master 2023 by TikTok \u0111\u1ec3 c\u00e1c kh\u00e1n gi\u1ea3 \u0111ang theo d\u00f5i ch\u01b0\u01a1ng tr\u00ecnh c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 tr\u1ef1c ti\u1ebfp b\u00ecnh ch\u1ecdn cho nh\u00e0 s\u00e1ng t\u1ea1o n\u1ed9i dung \u0111\u1ea7y \u0111\u1ee7 t\u1ed1 ch\u1ea5t tr\u1edf th\u00e0nh TikTok Master 2023. Sau khi t\u1ed5ng h\u1ee3p \u0111i\u1ec3m t\u1eeb BGK &amp; k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 t\u1eeb b\u00ecnh ch\u1ecdn c\u1ee7a kh\u00e1n gi\u1ea3 tr\u00ean trang ch\u1ee7 ch\u01b0\u01a1ng tr\u00ecnh, ch\u01b0\u01a1ng tr\u00ecnh s\u1ebd c\u00f4ng b\u1ed1 v\u00e0 trao gi\u1ea3i TikTok Master 2023 ngay trong Gala Night Master 2023 by TikTok.", "profileLarger": "https://p19-common-sign.tiktokcdn-us.com/tiktok-obj/e575d10aa161f68b74b5fa981b6a80fb.jpeg~tplv-tiktokx-origin.image?dr=9627&x-expires=1769778000&x-signature=dWm8dAbFYOb1JA0XEbxvk336x1k%3D&t=4d5b0474&ps=13740610&shp=81f88b70&shcp=9b759fb9&idc=useast5", "profileMedium": "https://p19-common-sign.tiktokcdn-us.com/tiktok-obj/e575d10aa161f68b74b5fa981b6a80fb.jpeg~tplv-tiktokx-origin.image?dr=9627&x-expires=1769778000&x-signature=dWm8dAbFYOb1JA0XEbxvk336x1k%3D&t=4d5b0474&ps=13740610&shp=81f88b70&shcp=9b759fb9&idc=useast5", "profileThumb": "https://p19-common-sign.tiktokcdn-us.com/tiktok-obj/e575d10aa161f68b74b5fa981b6a80fb.jpeg~tplv-tiktokx-origin.image?dr=9627&x-expires=1769778000&x-signature=dWm8dAbFYOb1JA0XEbxvk336x1k%3D&t=4d5b0474&ps=13740610&shp=81f88b70&shcp=9b759fb9&idc=useast5", "coverLarger": "https://p19-common-sign.tiktokcdn-us.com/tiktok-obj/d8e40a792bf3c104b5bfc21b4a74215c.png~tplv-tiktokx-origin.image?dr=9627&x-expires=1769778000&x-signature=pQYV3UDax7eIitm%2FoSPMbZ3NZOs%3D&t=4d5b0474&ps=13740610&shp=81f88b70&shcp=9b759fb9&idc=useast5", "coverMedium": "https://p19-common-sign.tiktokcdn-us.com/tiktok-obj/d8e40a792bf3c104b5bfc21b4a74215c.png~tplv-tiktokx-origin.image?dr=9627&x-expires=1769778000&x-signature=pQYV3UDax7eIitm%2FoSPMbZ3NZOs%3D&t=4d5b0474&ps=13740610&shp=81f88b70&shcp=9b759fb9&idc=useast5", "coverThumb": "https://p19-common-sign.tiktokcdn-us.com/tiktok-obj/d8e40a792bf3c104b5bfc21b4a74215c.png~tplv-tiktokx-origin.image?dr=9627&x-expires=1769778000&x-signature=pQYV3UDax7eIitm%2FoSPMbZ3NZOs%3D&t=4d5b0474&ps=13740610&shp=81f88b70&shcp=9b759fb9&idc=useast5"}, {"id": "1607741871345826", "title": "y15zrmalaysia", "desc": "", "profileLarger": "", "profileMedium": "", "profileThumb": "", "coverLarger": "", "coverMedium": "", "coverThumb": ""}, {"id": "80046873", "title": "y15zr", "desc": "", "profileLarger": "", "profileMedium": "", "profileThumb": "", "coverLarger": "", "coverMedium"